    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Why does Michael Lind (Op-Ed, Oct. 2) think that high heating-oil and prescription drug prices interest only people in the so-called swing-vote states? People in the Northeast and Northwest both get cold, and they also get sick. These are national issues.</p>
        <p>MARY S. DRIVER  Woodside, Queens, Oct. 2, 2000</p>
      </block>
